356
00:21:59,189 --> 00:22:02,199
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah tidak pernah memberimu banyak uang saku.</font>

357
00:22:02,199 --> 00:22:04,169
<font color=#FFFF00>(Musim Dingin tahun 2003)</font>

358
00:22:04,169 --> 00:22:05,469
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku mencarinya.</font>

359
00:22:05,629 --> 00:22:08,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau cari uang?
