360
00:22:08,639 --> 00:22:10,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Kepala, biar kami saja yang interogasi dia.</font>

361
00:22:10,939 --> 00:22:12,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa tidak menjawab pertanyaan Ayah?</font>

362
00:22:13,669 --> 00:22:14,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mencurinya?</font>

363
00:22:14,740 --> 00:22:17,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, aku hanya menggunakan raporku...</font>

364
00:22:17,040 --> 00:22:19,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa? Rapormu?</font>

365
00:22:20,010 --> 00:22:21,980
<font color=#FFFF00>(Rapor)</font>

366
00:22:27,859 --> 00:22:29,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku memanipulasi raporku.</font>

367
00:22:30,090 --> 00:22:32,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Yoo Bum hyung bilang dia
bisa dapat gaji banyak kalau kami melakukan itu.</font>

368
00:22:33,659 --> 00:22:35,060
<font color=#FFFF00>Kami membaginya jadi setengah.</font>

369
00:22:36,330 --> 00:22:40,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah, kau ini. Kenapa malah bohong soal nilaimu?</font>

370
00:22:40,570 --> 00:22:43,869
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayahmu pernah bahas soal
bagaimana nilaimu itu.</font>

371
00:22:44,540 --> 00:22:46,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Hei, minta maaf padanya.</font>

372
00:22:46,639 --> 00:22:48,709
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayah, tentang kecelakaan itu...</font>

373
00:22:52,810 --> 00:22:54,980
<font color=#FFFF00>- Kepala.
- Ah, Kepala.</font>

374
00:23:24,250 --> 00:23:26,409
<font color=#FFFF00>(Ibu)</font>

375
00:23:31,949 --> 00:23:33,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa ada sesuatu?</font>

376
00:23:33,350 --> 00:23:35,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau selalu melihat ponselmu.</font>

377
00:23:35,189 --> 00:23:38,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Kurasa malam ini aku harus pulang lebih awal.</font>

378
00:23:38,629 --> 00:23:40,530
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibuku membalas SMS-ku.</font>

379
00:23:40,530 --> 00:23:42,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa dia sakit?</font>

380
00:23:42,800 --> 00:23:44,429
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

381
00:23:45,100 --> 00:23:46,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya mendapatkan firasat buruk.</font>

382
00:23:50,399 --> 00:23:52,909
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku meniup lilin.</font>

383
00:23:53,510 --> 00:23:56,409
<font color=#FFFF00>Kompor... aku mematikannya.</font>

384
00:23:59,310 --> 00:24:00,379
<font color=#FFFF00>Pintu.</font>

385
00:24:03,619 --> 00:24:04,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku lupa mengunci pintu.</font>

386
00:24:05,020 --> 00:24:06,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa?</font>

387
00:24:06,919 --> 00:24:09,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak mengunci pintu. Aku harus cepat pulang ke rumah.</font>

388
00:24:09,689 --> 00:24:10,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu...</font>

389
00:24:11,859 --> 00:24:12,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Hong Joo-ssi.</font>

390
00:24:20,030 --> 00:24:22,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu, tolong angkatlah.</font>

391
00:24:24,639 --> 00:24:27,209
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebentar, Hong Joo.
Sebelumnya kau pernah jatuh dari salju?</font>

392
00:24:27,340 --> 00:24:28,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Belum, belum pernah.</font>

393
00:24:29,639 --> 00:24:32,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Ah, bagaimana ini?
Haruskah aku naik taksi?</font>

394
00:24:33,010 --> 00:24:34,619
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa aku panggil seseorang saja?</font>

395
00:24:36,119 --> 00:24:38,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Kemarikan kuncimu.
Biar aku yang nyetir.</font>

396
00:24:39,350 --> 00:24:41,659
<font color=#FFFF00>- Tapi...
- Aku sering mengemudi di bawah salju.</font>

397
00:24:41,659 --> 00:24:42,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan padaku. Aku yang menyetir.</font>

398
00:25:18,790 --> 00:25:19,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Permisi.</font>

399
00:25:31,409 --> 00:25:33,310
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa dia tidak mengangkatnya?</font>

400
00:25:33,310 --> 00:25:34,780
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah aku telepon polisi?</font>

401
00:25:36,939 --> 00:25:38,250
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yakin dia baik-baik saja.</font>

402
00:25:39,280 --> 00:25:41,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Halo? Ibu?</font>

403
00:25:42,480 --> 00:25:44,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa menelepon berkali-kali?</font>

404
00:25:47,919 --> 00:25:51,659
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukan, tadi di kafe
ponsel Ibu ketinggalan.</font>

405
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,359
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sebabnya Ibu mengabaikannya.</font>

406
00:25:55,459 --> 00:25:56,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Dasar bodoh.</font>

407
00:25:57,359 --> 00:25:59,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena sudah ditemukan,
Ibu sudah bisa bicara denganmu.</font>

408
00:25:59,429 --> 00:26:01,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Tadi anak muda menemukannya
dan mengembalikannya padaku.</font>

409
00:26:01,669 --> 00:26:03,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Lain kali jangan ketinggalan ponsel lagi...,</font>

410
00:26:03,139 --> 00:26:05,109
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan pastikan untuk segera mengambilnya!</font>

411
00:26:05,869 --> 00:26:08,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya. Aku akan segera pulang.</font>

412
00:26:12,010 --> 00:26:13,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Baguslah.</font>

413
00:26:13,310 --> 00:26:15,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau selalu khawatir ya pada ibumu?</font>

414
00:26:16,850 --> 00:26:17,919
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

415
00:26:22,619 --> 00:26:23,790
<font color=#FFFF00>Yoo Bum-ssi.</font>

416
00:26:27,090 --> 00:26:28,159
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau...</font>

417
00:26:29,600 --> 00:26:31,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau saja aku mengalami kecelakaan...,</font>

418
00:26:33,770 --> 00:26:35,770
<font color=#FFFF00>...maukah kau jaga ibuku baik-baik?</font>

419
00:26:35,770 --> 00:26:37,770
<font color=#FFFF00>Bicara apa kau?
Kecelakaan apa?</font>

420
00:26:38,139 --> 00:26:40,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu, aku tidak bicara tentang sekarang.</font>

421
00:26:40,909 --> 00:26:42,740
<font color=#FFFF00>Sesuatu seperti itu mungkin terjadi di masa depan.</font>

422
00:26:44,409 --> 00:26:45,449
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

423
00:26:45,850 --> 00:26:48,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak peduli yang terjadi,
aku akan pastikan...</font>

424
00:26:48,050 --> 00:26:50,320
<font color=#FFFF00>...menjaga ibumu.
Sudah 'kan?</font>

425
00:26:52,850 --> 00:26:55,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi, kau ini sungguh tidak apa-apa?
Kau tidak kelihatan baik.</font>

426
00:28:13,070 --> 00:28:14,199
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu.</font>

427
00:28:16,669 --> 00:28:17,840
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu.</font>

428
00:28:17,939 --> 00:28:19,909
<font color=#FFFF00>Omo, lihatlah. Dia sudah...</font>

429
00:28:19,909 --> 00:28:21,409
<font color=#FFFF00>- ...siuman.
- Ibu.</font>

430
00:28:21,409 --> 00:28:22,879
<font color=#FFFF00>- Omo.
- Omo.</font>

431
00:28:22,879 --> 00:28:24,149
<font color=#FFFF00>- Omo.
- Aggasi.</font>

432
00:28:24,149 --> 00:28:26,080
<font color=#FFFF00>- Bisa dengar kami?
- Ibuku...</font>

433
00:28:26,679 --> 00:28:27,780
<font color=#FFFF00>...ada di mana?</font>

434
00:28:27,780 --> 00:28:29,550
<font color=#FFFF00>- Cepat panggil dokter.
- Bisa kau melihatku?</font>

435
00:28:29,550 --> 00:28:31,290
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dia baik-baik saja?
- Omo.</font>

436
00:28:31,320 --> 00:28:32,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Yoo Bum-ssi.</font>

437
00:28:33,750 --> 00:28:34,859
<font color=#FFFF00>Cepat.</font>

438
00:28:34,859 --> 00:28:36,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Hong Joo.</font>

439
00:28:36,859 --> 00:28:38,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Nam Hong Joo-ssi, bisa lihat aku?</font>

440
00:28:39,290 --> 00:28:40,899
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa jari yang Anda lihat?</font>

441
00:28:41,100 --> 00:28:43,429
<font color=#FFFF00>- Astaga.
- Pasti keajaiban Natal.</font>

442
00:28:43,429 --> 00:28:45,270
<font color=#FFFF00>- Pasti begitu.
- Syukurlah.</font>

443
00:28:45,270 --> 00:28:46,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu di mana?</font>

444
00:28:46,899 --> 00:28:49,000
<font color=#FFFF00>- Dokter.
- Dia baik-baik saja, bukan?</font>

445
00:29:00,649 --> 00:29:01,719
<font color=#FFFF00>Rambutku...</font>

446
00:29:03,879 --> 00:29:05,219
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi dengan rambutku?</font>

447
00:29:09,760 --> 00:29:10,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Bibi.</font>

448
00:29:11,830 --> 00:29:13,030
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari ini tanggal berapa?</font>

449
00:29:13,159 --> 00:29:14,260
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari ini?</font>

450
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:17,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini malam natal.</font>

451
00:29:20,669 --> 00:29:21,969
<font color=#FFFF00>Hari Natal...</font>

452
00:29:22,869 --> 00:29:24,139
<font color=#FFFF00>...sudah lewat.</font>

453
00:29:25,109 --> 00:29:26,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu tiga bulan yang lalu.</font>

454
00:29:26,740 --> 00:29:30,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Aggasi, kau dirawat di sini selama 10 bulan.</font>

455
00:29:34,379 --> 00:29:35,379
<font color=#FFFF00>Bibi.</font>

456
00:29:37,050 --> 00:29:38,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu di mana?</font>

457
00:29:39,219 --> 00:29:40,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Bibi akan kasih tahu.</font>

458
00:29:42,060 --> 00:29:44,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Bibi akan kasih tahu
kalau sudah bangun.</font>

459
00:29:44,760 --> 00:29:46,290
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku sudah sepenuhnya bangun.</font>

460
00:29:47,699 --> 00:29:48,830
<font color=#FFFF00>Jadi katakan saja.</font>

461
00:29:53,600 --> 00:29:55,939
<font color=#FFFF00>Kuharap kau bangun lebih cepat.</font>

462
00:29:56,600 --> 00:29:58,909
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibumu melakukan yang terbaik untuk bertahan...</font>

463
00:29:59,240 --> 00:30:01,480
<font color=#FFFF00>...supaya bisa kembali sadar.</font>

464
00:30:03,709 --> 00:30:05,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudnya?</font>

465
00:30:07,409 --> 00:30:08,980
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang terjadi dengan Ibu?</font>

466
00:30:10,850 --> 00:30:13,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena kecelakaan yang kau alami...,</font>

467
00:30:15,119 --> 00:30:17,419
<font color=#FFFF00>...seseorang meninggal.</font>

468
00:30:18,560 --> 00:30:21,899
<font color=#FFFF00>Anakku! Anakku yang malang...</font>

469
00:30:22,659 --> 00:30:25,570
<font color=#FFFF00>Bawa dia kembali.
Bawa anakku kembali!</font>

470
00:30:30,600 --> 00:30:32,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Aigoo, putriku.</font>

471
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:36,810
<font color=#FFFF00>Bertahanlah sebentar, ya?
Ibu akan buatkan makanan lezat untukmu.</font>

472
00:30:37,709 --> 00:30:39,510
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia harus membayar uang pokok...</font>

473
00:30:39,850 --> 00:30:41,580
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan tagihan rumah sakitmu...,</font>

474
00:30:41,879 --> 00:30:45,219
<font color=#FFFF00>...jadi dia menjual semuanya
termasuk rumah dan restorannya.</font>

475
00:30:45,790 --> 00:30:47,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bekerja seharian sampai dia tidak tidur.</font>

476
00:30:50,060 --> 00:30:52,230
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia hanya memikirkan tentang kesadaranmu.</font>

477
00:30:52,790 --> 00:30:55,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu suatu hari, dia...</font>

478
00:31:12,310 --> 00:31:13,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia...</font>

479
00:31:14,850 --> 00:31:16,050
<font color=#FFFF00>...meninggal?</font>

480
00:31:16,719 --> 00:31:18,149
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya, dia meninggal.</font>

481
00:31:39,969 --> 00:31:41,980
<font color=#FFFF00>(Untuk putriku tersayang Hong Joo,)</font>

482
00:31:41,980 --> 00:31:44,449
<font color=#FFFF00>(Ada 25 juta Won dan 15 juta Won
di rekening tabungan Ibu.)</font>

483
00:31:44,449 --> 00:31:46,909
<font color=#FFFF00>(Ibu juga punya asuransi jiwa
yang bisa kau klaim.)</font>

484
00:31:46,909 --> 00:31:49,219
<font color=#FFFF00>(Jangan terpukul.)</font>

485
00:31:52,419 --> 00:31:53,520
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini pasti mimpi.</font>

486
00:31:55,359 --> 00:31:56,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa aku sedang bermimpi?</font>

487
00:31:56,919 --> 00:31:58,490
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan padaku kalau ini semua cuma mimpi.</font>

488
00:31:59,389 --> 00:32:00,459
<font color=#FFFF00>Ya?</font>

489
00:32:02,260 --> 00:32:03,800
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku harus bangun dari mimpi buruk ini.</font>

490
00:32:04,530 --> 00:32:06,000
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa aku tidak bisa bangun?</font>

491
00:32:09,439 --> 00:32:12,439
<font color=#FFFF00>Katakan padaku kalau ini hanya mimpi. Kumohon.</font>

492
00:32:13,469 --> 00:32:15,010
<font color=#FFFF00>Hong Joo.</font>

493
00:32:16,280 --> 00:32:17,609
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak suka mimpi ini.</font>

494
00:32:20,010 --> 00:32:21,280
<font color=#FFFF00>Bibi...</font>

495
00:32:22,750 --> 00:32:24,350
<font color=#FFFF00>Sadarkan dirimu.</font>

496
00:32:24,820 --> 00:32:27,020
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mungkin harus diadili.</font>

497
00:32:28,719 --> 00:32:29,959
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudnya?</font>

498
00:32:30,689 --> 00:32:32,129
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa aku harus diadili?</font>

499
00:32:32,990 --> 00:32:35,699
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bahkan tidak menyetir.
Kenapa harus aku?</font>

500
00:32:36,100 --> 00:32:37,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak menyetir?</font>

501
00:32:38,100 --> 00:32:40,270
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa aku terus dituduh
kalau aku penyebab kecelakaan itu?</font>

502
00:32:40,730 --> 00:32:42,369
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak menyetir.</font>

503
00:32:42,740 --> 00:32:45,540
<font color=#FFFF00>Kecelakaan itu bukan salahku!</font>

